          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多少，亦无一定，其大致几与《戏迷传》相仿佛矣。以李百岁、吕月樵等为最擅名，坤角恩晓峰亦善唱此剧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "根据《戏考》第九册整理"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哽哼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怪哉怪哉真怪哉，柳树上掉下烧饼来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小子孔怀，妹妹孔秀英。可恨我母亲其心不良，将我嫂嫂打在磨房挨磨，是我\n心中不忍，不免去至磨房，替我嫂嫂挨上几磨，就此前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哽哼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那不是妹子么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那不是哥哥么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹子快来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥等着，妹子来呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你干什么去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我抱柴火去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不让你过去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我打这边走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我拦住你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我打那边去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我挡住你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中间走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我与你堵上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "道路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要闹着玩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你手里拿的什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没什么。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看手。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个斗，两个斗，三个斗，四个斗，五个斗。看那只手。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "六个斗，七个斗，八个斗，九个斗，十个斗。两手一齐看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看见戏戏画没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么叫做戏戏画？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个喜鹊两个脑袋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在那里飞呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咦，热得不走，走到坝沟里去了。你走两步我看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，你看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走过去，这是什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "幺二三。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么幺二三？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鞭子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "干什么用的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打嫂子的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这个人没有良心，嫂子替你梳头裹脚，你还要打嫂子，不跟你玩呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不打嫂子呢。把这个抛去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们找嫂子玩去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行行去去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去去行行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "转弯抹角。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抹角转弯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要到，喂狗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要闹。进去喊嫂子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀、孔秀英",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂子！嫂子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂子不在家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猫叼去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂子出去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，出去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂子出去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们干什么玩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我妈说的，姑娘不给小子玩。给小子玩了要烂手指头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我妈说的，小子不给姑娘玩。给姑娘玩了要烂脚指头的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们回去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢着。我们兜圈子。到张园白相去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们进城，湖心亭吃茶去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们唱戏玩吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唱什么戏？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唱《庞德下书》。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁的元帅，谁的先行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的元帅，你的先行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的元帅，你的先行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，哪有个母元帅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，女元帅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错，女元帅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有行头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，戏房里行头多得很，随便你穿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那么哥哥等着，我妹子扮戏去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我妹子扮戏去呢。待我也扮起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀扮。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打吓打吓，怎么不打。哦，没有吃大烟呢，待我自家来。哒呛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生小生，我的儿子，唱老生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤王王世充，可恨曹操带兵前来，与孤争斗，不免修书一封，颁来孙二娘，大\n破天门阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在宝帐闷坏了秦叔宝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小罗成渭水河乱箭身亡。\n手提着没毛笔细写端详：\n拜上梁山小宋江。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "搭救孤王转汴梁。\n打发庞德走一程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庞德进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "一步儿来至在宝帐以上、上写拜上多拜上、你那里早发兵和将、一封书信忙修整、孔秀英",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "正在后帐把酒饮，\n忽听前帐传一声。\n元帅差我哪里行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅在上，庞德参见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迈步且把宝帐进、孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庞德听令。这有令箭一枝，走到北京城，颁来小叫天大战刘鸿声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "黄罗宝帐领将令，\n气坏老将黄汉升。\n阵前得罪二将军。\n俺的百步穿杨射他的盔缨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀扮龙套上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "食王的爵禄当报王的恩。\n再与师爷把话明：\n二不用虎将随后跟；\n匹马单刀取定军。\n军师大印输我身；\n愿将首级挂营门。\n来来来带过了爷的马能行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀允，带马，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "要把那定军一扫平。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英下。孔怀上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "龙争虎斗，这砂锅，何日打破？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天上有日头，山上有石头。海里有浪头，嘴里有舌头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤，乾德王赵。可恨欧阳藩，将孤诓下河东，围困七载，内无粮草，外无救兵，\n也曾命黄信四路打探，未见回报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打探军情事，报与主公知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报，探子告进。主公在上，探子参见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "探子打探哪路军情，一一奏来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听我奏你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢动手。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "探子报，主公听，一时一刻发来兵：苏秦六国为元帅，姚期马武为先行，主公\n不发人和马，看看杀到紫金城，看看杀到紫金城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报得好，报得妙，赏你二张假钞票。白日去洗澡，夜里陪我来睡觉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，且住。时才黄信报到，罗家山发来一哨人马，昨日鞭坠白龙，今日叫骂\n御营。看将起来，孤王的江山不久了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "探马儿止不住飞来报，\n他报道罗家山兵发一标。\n吓坏了御营中大小英豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀播鼓。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鼓又不响了。它又响了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "那一旁再撞景阳钟。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀撞钟。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钟也不响了。它又响了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "宗保儿搀为父病房来进，\n休惊动后堂内年迈太君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金牌宣，银牌诏，宣李广上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "乌鸦不住叫连天，\n叫得李广心胆惊。\n莫不是哪国起狼烟。\n莫不是我三弟酒席筵前打骂来。\n参王驾来问王安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "莫不是哪国贼犯境、是是是明白了、是与不是金殿上、孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣姚期见驾，吾皇万岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚皇兄，你可知罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣知罪。不知罪犯哪条？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚刚将郭太师打死，何言无罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启陛下：郭老太师也有一行大罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他得何罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "府门外私立三尺禁地，文官下轿，武将离鞍，但不知万岁可曾传旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寡人有言在先，未曾降旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁无旨，斩者无亏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个斩者无亏。\n绑坏了！\n殿角下绑的何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三子姚刚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦呀，不要绑坏孤的小爱卿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快松绑。\n领旨。\n谢万岁不斩之恩。\n非是寡人不斩于你，孤王有言在先，汉不斩姚，姚不反汉，将你发在湖北宛子\n城，你父子午门一别，下殿去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢万岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴才。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "万岁爷赦了姚霸林，\n好似枯木又逢春。\n再叫我儿听分明：\n儿不要提刀乱杀人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿来看！"
        },
        {
          "character": "手拉娇儿下龙庭、此去湖北万事忍、孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "为父的年迈苍苍白如银，姚刚我的儿吓，\n好一似瓦上霜风前烛能活几春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "爹爹不必泪悲惨，\n姚刚珠泪洒胸膛。\n在朝为官有什么好？\n半点不到有损伤。\n回府去拜上老萱堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹，我父！哎，爹爹吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚刚，霸林！哎，儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "金殿去了姚霸林，\n父子们相逢再不能。\n告职还乡乐安宁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英下。孔怀上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "得胜猫儿强似虎，\n败阵凤凰不如鸡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大元帅。\n有。\n看看什么旗号。\n遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "陈元吉打马到土台，\n只见儿郎闹该该。\n无敌将军康茂才。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃是康字旗号。\n待我谢天谢地。\n事到如今，还谢什么天地？\n大元帅，想那康茂才与孤有八拜之交，上前哀告，放你我君臣逃去，也未可知。\n臣杀不得了。\n不用你杀了，后面歇息去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听说来了康茂才，\n不由孤王笑颜开。\n问声贤弟可安泰。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "军师爷将令把咱催，\n站立在土台抖雄威。\n他道豪杰少计策。\n气得某家两眼黑。\n好汉英雄出在三国。\n要拿奸贼曹孟德。\n救命的铜锣点连点连紧紧催。\n后面跟随一伙贼。\n个个脸上带土灰。\n罗汉缺少袈裟披。\n事到头来埋怨谁？\n土台下来的尔是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "康贤弟比孤年纪小，\n耳不聋来眼不黑。\n为什么假装不认得？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀下，上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "辞别伯父把马跨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "陈宫心中似刀扎。\n好意反成恶冤家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丈，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你休埋怨我陈宫你只怨他。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔秀英下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孟德下马语发诈，\n陈宫为何泪如麻？\n急忙回家问根芽。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀下，孔秀英上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。俺曹庄不在家中，这贱人打骂老娘。不免唤他出来，相劝与他。若听还\n则罢了，倘若不听，俺举拳就打，吾提刀就杀。\n焦氏！焦氏！呔！贱人，走出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孔怀上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴在房中绣麒麟，\n忽然间想起了我们那个心腹上的人，常常奴家挂在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哟哟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "焦氏！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，饫死我呢。我道是谁，原来是我们那一口子他回来呢。\n曹郎你回来呢，你回来呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放老诚些。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫我出来，有何话讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搬张椅儿过来，为丈夫有话对你讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，搬张椅子过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔秀英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太近了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孔怀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太近呢。你也不是十七，我也不是十八，谁离不开谁。咱们就远着一点。"
